name: Ifeyinwa❤️
greetingText: I really like your name btw!
wishText: Heyyy Ifeyinwa, my one of a kind, You've touched my heart without the assistance of your hands & given me butterflies. 'till this day, I have yet to meet someone who made me feel the way you have made me feel. You made me feel and love like a kid again. I'll Love you always boo
